node.text:
Check out our video tour of this STUNNING build of New American Plan #260000RVC in Virginia! 🤩🏡⁠ by our friends @rivercitycustomhomes 
⁠
We love all of the contemporary details on this one - just look at that KITCHEN 😍 This plan is full of incredible features & offers an optionally finished 3rd floor!⁠
⁠
Quick Specs 👇⁠
📐 3,569 Sq Ft⁠⁠⁠⁠⁠⁠⁠⁠⁠⁠⁠⁠⁠⁠
🛏️ 5-6 Bedrooms⁠⁠⁠⁠⁠⁠⁠⁠⁠⁠⁠⁠⁠
🛁 4-5 Bathrooms⁠⁠⁠⁠⁠⁠⁠⁠⁠⁠⁠⁠⁠⁠
🚙 2 Car Garage⁠⁠⁠⁠⁠⁠⁠⁠⁠⁠⁠⁠⁠⁠
📏54'-4" Wide x 67'-1" Deep⁠⁠⁠⁠⁠⁠⁠⁠⁠⁠⁠⁠⁠⁠
 😍 What part are you most excited about?⁠
⁠
🌟LINK IN BIO🌟 or visit www.architecturaldesigns.com/260000RVC to check out the entire album & floor plan!⁠
⁠
⁠

node.text:
Take a tour Architectural Designs' charming 3-Bedroom Country Cottage house plan and floor plan #68505VR layout as we take a look around the exterior before stepping inside for a walkthrough tour of the interior!

See the full specs, floor plans and ordering information at this link: https://www.architecturaldesigns.com/68505VR

📐 2,095 Square Feet 
🛌 3 Bedrooms 
🛀 2.5 Baths 
🏠 2-Story 

We have construction documents available in PDF, CAD and Printed Set Formats!

node.title: 2100 SqFt Farmhouse Cottage Plan 68505VR in 3D w/ Interior Walkthrough!

Let us know in the comments below!! Follow @adhouseplans to find your next dream home plan!

node.text:
Anyone else think black exteriors are the ultimate fall/spooky season vibe? 🎃🍂👻⁠⁠
⁠⁠
This brand new Modern Farmhouse Plan #56508SM features an amazing gabled front elevation & a split bedroom layout - plus the master suite checks alllll the boxes ✅⁠⁠
⁠⁠
Here's a peek at the specs 🏡⁠⁠
📐 2,326 Sq Ft⁠⁠⁠⁠⁠
🛏️ 4 Bedrooms⁠⁠⁠⁠⁠
🛁 2.5 Bathrooms⁠⁠⁠⁠⁠
🚗 2 Car Garage⁠⁠⁠⁠⁠
📏 72'-10" Wide x 69'-6" Deep⁠⁠⁠⁠⁠
⁠⁠
We can't wait to see this one brought to life! Who will be the first to build this gorgeous Farmhouse? 🤩⁠⁠
⁠⁠
Check out the Link in Bio or visit www.architecturaldesigns.com/56508SM to learn more!⁠⁠
⁠⁠
#adhouseplans #blackexterior #modernfarmhouse #farmhouselove #farmhousestyle #curbappeal
